trans-unit.source: Represents a collision record resulting from a collision between forest trust records.
trans-unit.target: Представляет запись конфликтов, возникшем между записями доверия леса.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collision record from the underlying Active Directory Domain Services service.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает запись о конфликте из базовой службы доменных служб Active Directory.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the collision record resulting from a collision between forest trust records.
trans-unit.target: Объект <xref:System.String>содержащий запись о конфликте, возникшем между записями доверия леса.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref> value for the forest trust collision.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"> </xref> значение для конфликта доверия леса.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref> value indicating the collision type.
Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions"></xref> value for the forest trust collision.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions"> </xref> значение для конфликта доверия леса.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions"></xref> value that provides information about the collision when the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> type is <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Объект <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DomainCollisionOptions"> </xref> значение, предоставляющее сведения о конфликте при <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> тип — <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions"></xref> value for the forest trust collision.
trans-unit.target: Возвращает <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions"> </xref> значение для конфликта доверия леса.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions"></xref> value that provides information about the collision when the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> type is <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Объект <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameCollisionOptions"> </xref> значение, предоставляющее сведения о конфликте при <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustRelationshipCollision.CollisionType%2A?displayProperty=fullName> тип — <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ForestTrustCollisionType"> </xref>.
